text_logic_form: Point $V$ is a midpoint of one leg of the trapezoid $QRTU$.
Point $S$ is a midpoint of the other leg of the trapezoid $QRTU$.

The length of the line $UT$ is $12$ units.
Find the length of the line $QR$.
